Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:05.07,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about what happened earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.07,0:00:08.40,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,We put so much effort into the welcome party, yet we couldn't make it more exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.40,0:00:09.98,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,You call that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:11.30,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,"Couldn't"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.30,0:00:15.17,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,To suddenly see the news about the culprit behind Prince Clovis's murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.17,0:00:18.04,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,It was unbearable even for me, the great Milly-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.04,0:00:20.23,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really mind about that but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.06,0:00:23.04,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we in the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:25.42,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, why did I have to come along?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.42,0:00:28.17,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,I already had a shower just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.17,0:00:31.37,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well. This is another round of getting to know each other better.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.37,0:00:35.13,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,The close contact between na-ke-d fri-ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:41.43,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Also, if you wear Lelouch's clothes back just like that, someone will get really pissed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.43,0:00:42.54,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that so, Shirley?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.97,0:00:45.61,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,P-President, what are you saying all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.42,0:00:51.90,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,But, wasn't Lulu acting strangely after he saw the news?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.90,0:00:54.24,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,It seemed that his heart had wandered off.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.24,0:00:56.13,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Nana-chan was around.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.13,0:00:58.96,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that was unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.96,0:01:03.82,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,The way he treats me and the way he treats his sister are completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.82,0:01:07.68,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's in love with his sister after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.68,0:01:09.08,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,That's going to be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.08,0:01:10.73,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you looking at me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.75,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,You have a wonderful body as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.75,0:01:18.03,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that athletic build gives off a seductive and alluring feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.03,0:01:19.61,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please stop looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.61,0:01:22.09,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine right? Not as if you'll lose anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.09,0:01:23.27,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lose something!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.27,0:01:26.48,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, President, isn't your body the most curvaceous?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:28.48,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.07,0:01:32.30,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, Milly-chan, everyone will catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.30,0:01:35.80,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...Y-You are Nina-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.08,0:01:38.82,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,You look completly different without your glasses on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.82,0:01:39.96,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.96,0:01:43.13,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,All this time, I've been telling her to change to contacts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.13,0:01:44.63,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,This girl is really...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.63,0:01:46.98,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, Milly-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.98,0:01:48.33,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,"All this time"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.33,0:01:50.15,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,We grew up together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.15,0:01:54.18,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,My grandfather worked in Milly-chan's grandfather's company.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.18,0:01:56.12,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,They were developing KnightMares.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.12,0:01:57.78,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Ashford...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:02:01.99,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Did they develop the Ganymede and Ion series?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.99,0:02:04.75,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you know about it. That's surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.75,0:02:06.72,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,They were machines that didn't proceed past the testing phrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:11.53,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, erm... I read about them from somewhere... That's all I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.43,0:02:16.00,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Well, in the end they weren't put into actual production.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.00,0:02:20.15,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,The development costs started to pile up and the company eventually closed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.15,0:02:22.22,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Milly-chan, I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.22,0:02:23.83,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my grandfather's fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:26.88,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've already told you it's not due to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.88,0:02:30.33,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,The main reason is because of Grandfather's extravagance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.33,0:02:31.56,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Extravagance?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.56,0:02:34.13,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He loved to organize those old fashion parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:38.55,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,They would go on nosily for days and nights without any good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:42.64,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's thanks to the contacts he established back then that we were able to create
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.64,0:02:45.50,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,a presence in this country and even set up an academy here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:50.16,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,But President, you sure inherited the party-loving part from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.16,0:02:51.33,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:55.28,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,We can only do such silly things while we're still students.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.28,0:02:59.34,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Kallen-san, are you free after school the day after tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.34,0:03:00.98,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,The day after tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.98,0:03:03.23,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,I think... No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.23,0:03:04.62,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to do the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:05.71,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.71,0:03:09.93,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,1-1600hrs... s-sort of need to go to the Tokyo Tower...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:13.72,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we can do it now too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.72,0:03:16.19,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Kallen-san, I want to know your three sizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:16.97,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.97,0:03:20.54,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,We often need to make costumes for parties or events. I need it for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.54,0:03:23.40,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,In order words... a cosplay show?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:24.34,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:25.00,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:28.66,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,No need to be shy. We are all women.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.66,0:03:29.94,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,So... Shirley!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:31.58,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Kallen...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.58,0:03:32.50,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Hold her back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:37.14,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,This is... My, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.14,0:03:39.99,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please... stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.99,0:03:43.21,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Kallen, you are pretty strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.21,0:03:45.84,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Quite a nice body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.84,0:03:48.03,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you say that you're weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:51.50,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please... stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:55.09,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,That is charming in its own way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.12,0:03:58.01,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.01,0:04:00.41,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.09,0:04:03.57,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,NO!!!
